### 9. General Fixture — `_logger` field (line 11, 19)

`_logger` is initialized in `[TestInitialize]` but **no test method in the class uses it**. Every test pays the cost of creating a `FakeLogger` for nothing.

**Fix:** Remove it. Add it back only in tests that need it.

